#. <section class="sutta" id="sn2.26"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.26:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.26:0.2"
msgid "3. Nānātitthiyavagga"
msgstr "3. Various Sectarians"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.26:0.3"
msgid "26. Rohitassasutta"
msgstr "26. With Rohitassa"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.143"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.26:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn2.26:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho rohitasso devaputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Standing to one side, the god Rohitassa said to the Buddha:"

#. VAR: na jīyati na mīyati → na jiyyati na miyyati (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "sn2.26:1.3"
msgid ""
"“yattha nu kho, bhante, na jāyati na jīyati na mīyati na cavati na "
"upapajjati, sakkā nu kho so, bhante, gamanena lokassa anto ñātuṃ vā daṭṭhuṃ "
"vā pāpuṇituṃ vā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, is it possible to know or see or reach the end of the world by "
"traveling to a place where there’s no being born, growing old, dying, "
"passing away, or being reborn?”"

msgctxt "sn2.26:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Yattha kho, āvuso, na jāyati na jīyati na mīyati na cavati na upapajjati, "
"nāhaṃ taṃ gamanena lokassa antaṃ ñāteyyaṃ daṭṭheyyaṃ patteyyanti vadāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend, I say it’s not possible to know or see or reach the end of the "
"world by traveling to a place where there’s no being born, growing old, "
"dying, passing away, or being reborn.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.26:2.1"
msgid "“Acchariyaṃ, bhante, abbhutaṃ, bhante."
msgstr "“It’s incredible, sir, it’s amazing,"

msgctxt "sn2.26:2.2"
msgid "Yāvasubhāsitamidaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā:"
msgstr "how well said this was by Master Gotama."

msgctxt "sn2.26:2.3"
msgid ""
"‘yattha kho, āvuso, na jāyati na jīyati na mīyati na cavati na upapajjati, "
"nāhaṃ taṃ gamanena lokassa antaṃ ñāteyyaṃ daṭṭheyyaṃ patteyyanti vadāmī’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.62"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.144"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.26:3.1"
msgid ""
"Bhūtapubbāhaṃ, bhante, rohitasso nāma isi ahosiṃ bhojaputto iddhimā "
"vehāsaṅgamo."
msgstr ""
"Once upon a time, I was a hermit called Rohitassa, son of Bhoja. I was a sky-"
"walker with psychic power."

#. VAR: daḷhadhammā → daḷhadhammo (si, s1-3, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn2.26:3.2"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, evarūpo javo ahosi; seyyathāpi nāma daḷhadhammā "
"dhanuggaho susikkhito katahattho katayoggo katūpāsano lahukena asanena "
"appakasireneva tiriyaṃ tālacchāyaṃ atipāteyya."
msgstr ""
"I was as fast as a light arrow easily shot across the shadow of a palm tree "
"by a well-trained expert archer with a strong bow."

msgctxt "sn2.26:3.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, evarūpo padavītihāro ahosi; seyyathāpi nāma puratthimā "
"samuddā pacchimo samuddo."
msgstr ""
"My stride was such that it could span from the eastern ocean to the western "
"ocean."

msgctxt "sn2.26:3.4"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, evarūpaṃ icchāgataṃ uppajji:"
msgstr "This wish came to me:"

msgctxt "sn2.26:3.5"
msgid "‘ahaṃ gamanena lokassa antaṃ pāpuṇissāmī’ti."
msgstr "‘I will reach the end of the world by traveling.’"

# Note that the phrase evarūpena javena samannāgatassa evarūpena ca padavītihārena is in the previous segment in the AN version.
msgctxt "sn2.26:3.6"
msgid ""
"So khvāhaṃ, bhante, evarūpena javena samannāgato evarūpena ca "
"padavītihārena, aññatreva asitapītakhāyitasāyitā aññatra uccārapassāvakammā "
"aññatra niddākilamathapaṭivinodanā vassasatāyuko vassasatajīvī vassasataṃ "
"gantvā appatvāva lokassa antaṃ antarāva kālaṅkato."
msgstr ""
"Having such speed and stride, I traveled for my whole lifespan of a hundred "
"years—pausing only to eat and drink, go to the toilet, and sleep to dispel "
"weariness—and I passed away along the way, never reaching the end of the "
"world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.26:4.1"
msgid "Acchariyaṃ, bhante, abbhutaṃ, bhante."
msgstr "It’s incredible, sir, it’s amazing,"

msgctxt "sn2.26:4.2"
msgid "Yāvasubhāsitamidaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā:"
msgstr "how well said this was by Master Gotama:"

msgctxt "sn2.26:4.3"
msgid ""
"‘yattha kho, āvuso, na jāyati na jīyati na mīyati na cavati na upapajjati, "
"nāhaṃ taṃ gamanena lokassa antaṃ ñāteyyaṃ daṭṭheyyaṃ patteyyanti vadāmī’”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Reverend, I say it’s not possible to know or see or reach the end of the "
"world by traveling to a place where there’s no being born, growing old, "
"dying, passing away, or being reborn.’”"

# repetition of previous segment apparently omitted by mistake.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.145"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.26:5.1"
msgid ""
"“Na kho panāhaṃ, āvuso, appatvā lokassa antaṃ dukkhassa antakiriyaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""
"“But Reverend, I also say there’s no making an end of suffering without "
"reaching the end of the world."

msgctxt "sn2.26:5.2"
msgid ""
"Api ca khvāhaṃ, āvuso, imasmiṃyeva byāmamatte kaḷevare sasaññimhi samanake "
"lokañca paññapemi lokasamudayañca lokanirodhañca lokanirodhagāminiñca "
"paṭipadanti."
msgstr ""
"For it is in this fathom-long carcass with its perception and mind that I "
"describe the world, its origin, its cessation, and the practice that leads "
"to its cessation."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.26:6.1"
msgid "Gamanena na pattabbo,"
msgstr "The end of the world can never"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.26:6.2"
msgid "lokassanto kudācanaṃ;"
msgstr "be reached by traveling."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.26:6.3"
msgid "Na ca appatvā lokantaṃ,"
msgstr "But without reaching the end of the world,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.26:6.4"
msgid "dukkhā atthi pamocanaṃ."
msgstr "there’s no release from suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.26:7.1"
msgid "Tasmā have lokavidū sumedho,"
msgstr "So a clever person, understanding the world,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.26:7.2"
msgid "Lokantagū vusitabrahmacariyo;"
msgstr "has completed the spiritual journey, and gone to the end of the world."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.26:7.3"
msgid "Lokassa antaṃ samitāvi ñatvā,"
msgstr "A peaceful one, knowing the end of the world,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.26:7.4"
msgid "Nāsīsati lokamimaṃ parañcā”ti."
msgstr "does not hope for this world or the next.”"
